pageProduct.name: Wanderlust Energy Mushroom 75g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

An organic 5 mushroom health blend with iron derived from Spirulina to support energy production.

Wanderlust Energy Mushroom is a consciously created, organic 5 mushroom wholefood health blend. With iron derived from Spirulina to support energy production, reduce fatigue and assist healthy oxygen transportation.

Size: 75 g NET

Ingredients

INGREDIENTS: Organic Spirulina Powder* (51.7%), Wanderlust Organic Mushroom Blend* (48.3%) [Shiitake mushroom powder*, Enokitake mushroom powder*, Oyster mushroom powder*, Trumpet mushroom powder*, Brown rice powder*, Maitake mushroom powder*].

*Organic ingredients

No added gluten, dairy, lactose, soy, egg, artificial colours or artificial flavours. Suitable for vegetarians and vegans.

Directions

SERVING SUGGESTION: Mix 3.7 g (1 teaspoon) in 200 mL of water or juice. Alternatively, add to a smoothie or sprinkle onto salad, soups or meals.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry
place away from direct heat
and sunlight. Do not use if
inner seal is missing or broken.
